<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.7">
<l>neñciṉāl niṉaintum vāyiṉāl moḻintum</l>
<l>nītiyal lātaṉa ceytum</l>
<l>tuñciṉār cellun toṉṉeṟi kēṭṭē</l>
<l>tuḷaṅkiṉēṉ viḷaṅkaṉi muṉintāy</l>
<l>vañcaṉē ṉaṭiyēṉ neñciṉil piriyā</l>
<l>vāṉavā tāṉavark keṉṟum</l>
<l>nañcaṉē vantuṉ tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having contemplated in my mind, spoken with my lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">and practiced injustices,</l>
<l>I trembled, hearing of the ancient path where</l>
<l rend="indent">those who sleep [forever] have gone.</l>
<l>You who savaged the woodapple [tree], I am a fraud;</l>
<l rend="indent">beloved of my heart, celestial [lord], forever bane of the Dānavas,</l>
<l>Coming [here], I, [your] servant, took refuge at your divine feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
